entries.s_32: You're the one Qual'do Herm said was coming? Good. The Empire is experimenting with some sort of concentrated energy compound. It's unstable and dangerous. I need you to recover a sample of that compound as well as development notes and the original design overview. I would get them, but I lack the security clearance and don't have your military prowess. Or at the very least, don't have your courage.
entries.s_34: Shhhh! Be quiet. Someone might hear us.
